@startuml
hide footbox
actor Client
boundary "API Gateway\n(AWS API Gateway)" as APIGW
participant "Identity & Access Control" as IAM
participant "Keycloak\n(External Auth)" as Keycloak
participant "Chat Registry" as ChatReg
participant "Message Store" as MsgStore
queue "Outbox" as Outbox
queue "Event Bus\n(Amazon EventBridge)" as EventBus
participant "Realtime Gateway\n(AWS API Gateway SSE)" as RTGW
participant "Specialist Router" as Router
participant "Itinerary Specialist" as Specialist
participant "History Query" as History
database "Conversation Cache\n(AWS ElastiCache)" as Cache
participant "Tool Adapter" as Tools
participant "Specialist Data Store" as SpecDB
database "Specialist Blob Storage\n(Amazon S3)" as SpecBlob

== User asks for an itinerary ==
Client -> APIGW : Send message (HTTPS)\n\"Quiero 5 días en Japón, presupuesto 1500€, me gusta comida y templos.\"
APIGW -> IAM : Validate token
IAM -> Keycloak : OIDC/OAuth2
Keycloak --> IAM : OK
IAM --> APIGW : OK
APIGW -> ChatReg : Validate chat
ChatReg --> APIGW : OK
APIGW -> MsgStore : Write user message
MsgStore -> Outbox : Append event
Outbox -> EventBus : Publish
EventBus -> RTGW : Fan-out
RTGW --> Client : SSE update

EventBus -> Router : Route by chat type
Router -> Specialist : Invoke (gRPC/HTTP)

Specialist -> History : Read history
History -> Cache : Read cache
alt Cache miss
  History -> Cache : Warm cache
end

Specialist -> Tools : tool_call (flight_search, hotel_search, poi_search)
Tools --> Specialist : tool_result
Specialist -> SpecDB : Store tool_call/tool_result

Specialist -> SpecDB : Create itinerary (itinerary_id=it_123)
Specialist -> MsgStore : Write assistant summary\n\"Listo, aquí tienes un itinerario de 5 días.\" + meta.itinerary_id=it_123
MsgStore -> Outbox : Append event
Outbox -> EventBus : Publish
EventBus -> RTGW : Fan-out
RTGW --> Client : SSE update

== Client fetches itinerary details ==
Client -> APIGW : GET /itinerary/it_123
APIGW -> IAM : Validate token
IAM -> Keycloak : OIDC/OAuth2
Keycloak --> IAM : OK
IAM --> APIGW : OK
APIGW -> Specialist : Fetch itinerary
Specialist -> SpecDB : Read itinerary details
Specialist --> APIGW : Itinerary details\nDay 1: Tokyo (Senso-ji, Asakusa, food)\nDay 2: Kyoto (Fushimi Inari, Gion)\nDay 3: Nara (Todai-ji)\nDay 4: Osaka (Dotonbori)\nDay 5: Tokyo (Shibuya, shopping)
APIGW --> Client : Itinerary details

== Client edits itinerary ==
Client -> APIGW : POST /itinerary/it_123/edit\n\"Cambia el día 2 a Kyoto y añade un tour gastronómico.\"
APIGW -> IAM : Validate token
IAM -> Keycloak : OIDC/OAuth2
Keycloak --> IAM : OK
IAM --> APIGW : OK
APIGW -> ChatReg : Validate chat
ChatReg --> APIGW : OK
APIGW -> Specialist : Execute edit action
Specialist -> SpecDB : Update itinerary
Specialist -> MsgStore : Write visible summary\n\"He actualizado el Día 2 a Kyoto y añadí un tour gastronómico.\"
MsgStore -> Outbox : Append event
Outbox -> EventBus : Publish
EventBus -> RTGW : Fan-out
RTGW --> Client : SSE update

@enduml
